:: A Small Step {"position":"1525,575","size":"100,100"}
<div class="story">
  <!-- Set the text to show -->
  (set: $typewriterText to
  "Jeff's usual morning routine starts with feeling tired and grabbing his coffee, but today is different...
  
  As he reaches for the coffee pot, he takes a pause . . . 
  Jeff makes a sincere, conscious effort to think about why he's always so exhausted.
  
  He stops himself and instead makes a glass of water and completes a few stretches (not quite 15 mins, but close enough), and is surprised by how energsed it makes him feel.

On arrival at work...Jeff is faced with another of his usual decisions...

Does he grab a healthier breakfast choice of porridge, or the usual coffee and pastry?
")

