:: A new day {"position":"1250,550","size":"100,100"}
<div class="story">
  <!-- Set the text to show -->
  (set: $typewriterText to "Each morning, Jeff's alarm rings, and he wakes up feeling tired and lethargic, dreading the workday ahead. In his rush to get out the door, he habitually skips breakfast at home, opting to rely on coffee to kickstart his day. This caffeine boost is accompanied by a sugary pastry (because it’s right there...so why not), offering a fleeting sense of alertness and satisfaction.
As Jeff arrives at the office, he grabs another coffee on his way through, as he always does, saving himself from the need to get up again later in the morning. The initial rush fades quickly, leaving him feeling hungry and sluggish. Fortunately, elevenses is just around the corner and to maintain some semblance of energy, he grabs himself just one more coffee and a biscuit to see him through the morning.")
