  (set: $typewriterText to "By the time lunch rolls around, Jeff, a hard-working and dedicated employee, hasn't made as much progress on his work as he had hoped. Feeling stressed and pressed for time, he rushes out to grab his usual lunch: a chicken and bacon sandwich, a bag of steak flavoured McCoys, a chocolate bar, and a seemingly innocent peach iced tea (fruit products area healthier, right?).

He returns to his desk to eat, continuing to work through what should be his lunch break. 

