:: Observation {"position":"1400,900","size":"100,100"}
<div class="story">
  <!-- Set the text to show -->
  (set: $typewriterText to
  "After the usual formalities, Sarah pauses for a moment and eventually breaks the silence and asks 'Jeff, I've been meaning to check in with you recently. You seem different lately. Is everything okay?'

Not quite sure what she's reffering to, Jeff enquires 'Different? In what way?'

Well, it's just that you used to be so energetic and on top of things, and now it feels like you're constantly tired and stressed. Your work has been slipping, and you've been absent quite a bit, Sarah explains.

Jeff takes a moment to reflect - 'Errr, I guess I haven't really stopped to think about it! It does perhaps feel like I've been on autopilot for a while now.'

Sarah continues, 'I understand that we all go through tough times, but I care about you, and I've seen you struggling. Is there something going on? Can I help in any way?'

Taking a further moment, Jeff looks at his reflection in the glass... he realises how he may have let himself go and is perhaps in a bit of a rut.
He conceeds, 'To be honest, I agree. I do feel constantly tired, and I've definitely put  weight on. It's like I'm stuck in this endless cycle! The work and stress feed the habits, that I know aren't great, and I guess the habits feed the stress'.

Well, Sarah suggests, it's never too late to make a change, Jeff, and you don't have to go through this alone! We're here to support you. Let's figure out a plan to help you get back on track and find balance in your life. ")

  <!-- Display (call) the Typewriter passage -->
  (display: "Typewriter")
</div>

